<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>CLOSER LORD TO THEE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa Nang ka hun naih hi,
 Ka hun naih zel ie;
 Na tha limnuoi bitna mun,
 Ah umzing ing ka;
 Gitloh, ginlah huihhat in,
 Muntin ah ei mut mahleh;
 Eipui in guolzo ing ka,
 Lalpa ka hun naih.

[V2]
 2. Ka naih Lalpa ka thagau,
 Suongpi leh Bitna;
 Thepna tui kinawk mahleh,
 Lung lau diek puong ka;
 Huihpi'n ei sulau puona,
 Ei suknat theihloh ding ziek;
 Na hehpih khuta kinga'n,
 Lalpa ka hun naih.

[V3]
 3. Ka hun naih deuh deuh zel hi,
 Panpih ka chawlhna;
 Zaidam in ziehi ka ngen,
 &quot;Pa nang thu hi hen,&quot;
 Lungkham laiin ngilh puo'ng ka,
 Lungkham meipi zi'n laiin;
 Hehpih na'n ei hihhat in,
 Lalpa ka hun naih.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>89</hymn_number>
</song>